ix</p>\n\n<p><strong>0.4.3.6 - November 5, 2014</strong></p>\n\n<p>fixed Windows issue.</p>\n\n<p><strong>0.4.3.5 - July 15, 2014</strong></p>\n\n<p>fixed a case of message: \'PHP Notice: Trying to get property of non-object</p>\n\n<p><strong>0.4.3.4 - November 19, 2013</strong></p>\n\n<p>Unable to uninstall because of wrong filename.</p>\n\n<p><strong>0.4.3.2 - June 19, 2013</strong></p>\n\n<p>minor bug fix.</p>\n\n<p><strong>0.4.3.1 - June 15, 2013</strong></p>\n\n<p>some fix</p>\n\n<p><strong>0.4.3 - June 11, 2013</strong></p>\n\n<p>create 404.html.\nadded some filter (and action) hook.</p>\n\n<p><strong>0.4.2.1 - June 7, 2013</strong></p>\n\n<p>minor bug fix.</p>\n\n<p><strong>0.4.2 - June 7, 2013</strong></p>\n\n<p>source code refactoring</p>\n\n<p><strong>0.4.0 - May 14, 2013</strong></p>\n\n<p>Initial release.</p>\";s:3:\"faq\";s:11:\"<p>none</p>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:56:\"Transform your WordPress into static websites and blogs.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:61:\"http://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/staticpress.0.4.3.7.zip\";s:4:\"tags\";a:1:{s:6:\"static\";s:6:\"static\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:238:\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_donations&#038;business=9S8AJCY7XB8F4&#038;lc=JP&#038;item_name=WordPress%20Plugins&#038;item_number=wp%2dplugins&#038;currency_code=JPY&#038;bn=PP%2dDonationsBF%3abtn_donate_SM%2egif%3aNonHosted\";}\";s:8:\"response\";a:2:{s:4:\"code\";i:200;s:7:\"message\";s:2:\"OK\";}s:7:\"cookies\";a:0:{}s:8:\"filename\";N;}','yes'),(35318,'db_upgraded','','yes'),(39205,'_site_transient_update_core','O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"updates\";a:2:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:8:\"response\";s:6:\"latest\";s:8:\"download\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/release/ja/wordpress-4.1.zip\";s:6:\"locale\";s:2:\"ja\";s:8:\"packages\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"full\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/release/ja/wordpress-4.1.zip\";s:10:\"no_content\";b:0;s:11:\"new_bundled\";b:0;s:7:\"partial\";b:0;s:8:\"rollback\";b:0;}s:7:\"curr